#: ../../docs/user_manual/print_layout/overview_layout.rst:5
msgid "Overview of the Print Layout"
msgstr "Pregled rasporeda za štampu"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/print_layout/overview_layout.rst:12
msgid ""
"The print layout provides growing layout and printing capabilities. It "
"allows you to add elements such as the QGIS 2D or 3D map canvas, text "
"labels, images, legends, scale bars, basic shapes, arrows, attribute and "
"simple tables, elevation profiles and HTML frames... You can size, group, "
"align, position and rotate each element and adjust their properties to "
"create your layout."
msgstr ""
"Raspored za štampu pruža sve bogatije mogućnosti raspoređivanja i štampanja."
" Omogućava vam da dodate elemente kao što su QGIS 2D ili 3D platno karte, "
"tekstualni natpisi, slike, legende, razmernici, osnovni oblici, strelice, "
"atributske i jednostavne tabele, visinski profili i HTML okviri... Svaki "
"element možete dimenzionisati, grupisati, poravnati, pozicionirati i "
"rotirati i podesiti njegova svojstva da biste napravili svoj raspored."

#: ../../docs/user_manual/print_layout/overview_layout.rst:18
msgid ""
"The layout can be printed or exported to image formats, PostScript, PDF or "
"to SVG. You can save the layout as a template and load it again in another "
"session. Finally, generating several maps based on a template can be done "
"through the atlas generator."
msgstr ""
"Raspored se može odštampati ili izvesti u formate slike, PostScript, PDF ili"
" SVG. Raspored možete sačuvati kao šablon i ponovo ga učitati u drugoj "
"sesiji. Najzad, generisanje više karata na osnovu šablona može se obaviti "
"pomoću generatora atlasa."

#: ../../docs/user_manual/print_layout/overview_layout.rst:26
msgid "Sample Session for beginners"
msgstr "Primer sesije za početnike"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/print_layout/overview_layout.rst:28
msgid ""
"Before you start to work with the print layout, you need to load some raster"
" or vector layers in the QGIS map canvas and adapt their properties to suit "
"your own convenience. After everything is rendered and symbolized to your "
"liking, click the |newLayout| :sup:`New Print Layout` icon in the "
":guilabel:`Project` toolbar or choose :menuselection:`Project -->` "
"|newLayout| :menuselection:`New Print Layout`. You will be prompted to "
"choose a title for the new layout."
msgstr ""
"Pre nego što počnete da radite sa rasporedom za štampu, potrebno je da "
"učitate neke rasterske ili vektorske slojeve u QGIS platno karte i "
"prilagodite njihova svojstva prema sopstvenim potrebama. Kada je sve "
"iscrtano i simbolizovano po vašoj želji, kliknite na ikonu |newLayout| "
":sup:`Novi raspored za štampu` u paleti alatki :guilabel:`Projekat` ili "
"izaberite :menuselection:`Projekat -->` |newLayout| :menuselection:`Novi "
"raspored za štampu`. Biće vam zatraženo da izaberete naslov za novi "
"raspored."

#: ../../docs/user_manual/print_layout/overview_layout.rst:898
msgid "newLayout"
msgstr "newLayout"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/print_layout/overview_layout.rst:36
msgid ""
"To demonstrate how to create a map please follow the next instructions."
msgstr "Da bismo pokazali kako se pravi karta, pratite sledeća uputstva."

#: ../../docs/user_manual/print_layout/overview_layout.rst:38
msgid ""
"On the left side, select the |addMap| :sup:`Add map` toolbar button and draw"
" a rectangle on the canvas holding down the left mouse button. Inside the "
"drawn rectangle the QGIS map view to the canvas."
msgstr ""
"Sa leve strane izaberite dugme palete alatki |addMap| :sup:`Dodaj kartu` i "
"nacrtajte pravougaonik na platnu držeći pritisnut levi taster miša. Unutar "
"nacrtanog pravougaonika prikazaće se QGIS prikaz karte na platnu."

#: ../../docs/user_manual/print_layout/overview_layout.rst:830
msgid "addMap"
msgstr "addMap"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/print_layout/overview_layout.rst:41
msgid ""
"Select the |scaleBar| :sup:`Add scalebar` toolbar button and click with the "
"left mouse button on the print layout canvas. A scalebar will be added to "
"the canvas."
msgstr ""
"Izaberite dugme palete alatki |scaleBar| :sup:`Dodaj razmernik` i kliknite "
"levim tasterom miša na platno rasporeda za štampu. Razmernik će biti dodat "
"na platno."

#: ../../docs/user_manual/print_layout/overview_layout.rst:918
msgid "scaleBar"
msgstr "scaleBar"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/print_layout/overview_layout.rst:45
msgid ""
"Select the |addLegend| :sup:`Add legend` toolbar button and draw a rectangle"
" on the canvas holding down the left mouse button. Inside the drawn "
"rectangle the legend will be drawn."
msgstr ""
"Izaberite dugme palete alatki |addLegend| :sup:`Dodaj legendu` i nacrtajte "
"pravougaonik na platnu držeći pritisnut levi taster miša. Unutar nacrtanog "
"pravougaonika biće iscrtana legenda."

#: ../../docs/user_manual/print_layout/overview_layout.rst:826
msgid "addLegend"
msgstr "addLegend"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/print_layout/overview_layout.rst:48
msgid ""
"Select the |select| :sup:`Select/Move item` icon to select the map on the "
"canvas and move it a bit."
msgstr ""
"Izaberite ikonu |select| :sup:`Izaberi/pomeri stavku` da biste izabrali "
"kartu na platnu i malo je pomerili."

#: ../../docs/user_manual/print_layout/overview_layout.rst:920
msgid "select"
msgstr "select"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/print_layout/overview_layout.rst:50
msgid ""
"While the map item is still selected you can also change the size of the map"
" item. Click while holding down the left mouse button, in a white little "
"rectangle in one of the corners of the map item and drag it to a new "
"location to change its size."
msgstr ""
"Dok je stavka karte i dalje izabrana, možete promeniti i veličinu stavke "
"karte. Kliknite držeći pritisnut levi taster miša na beli pravougaonik u "
"jednom od uglova stavke karte i prevucite ga na novu lokaciju da biste "
"promenili njenu veličinu."

#: ../../docs/user_manual/print_layout/overview_layout.rst:54
msgid ""
"Click the :guilabel:`Item Properties` panel on the left down side and find "
"the setting for the orientation. Change the value of the setting "
":guilabel:`Map orientation` to '15.00°'. You should see the orientation of "
"the map item change."
msgstr ""
"Kliknite na panel :guilabel:`Svojstva stavke` u donjem levom delu i "
"pronađite podešavanje za orijentaciju. Promenite vrednost podešavanja "
":guilabel:`Orijentacija karte` na „15.00°“. Trebalo bi da vidite kako se "
"orijentacija stavke karte menja."

#: ../../docs/user_manual/print_layout/overview_layout.rst:58
msgid ""
"Now, you can print or export your print layout to image formats, PDF or to "
"SVG with the export tools in :menuselection:`Layout` menu."
msgstr ""
"Sada možete odštampati ili izvesti svoj raspored za štampu u formate slike, "
"PDF ili SVG pomoću alatki za izvoz u meniju :menuselection:`Raspored`."

#: ../../docs/user_manual/print_layout/overview_layout.rst:60
msgid ""
"Finally, you can save your print layout within the project file with the "
"|fileSave| :sup:`Save Project` button."
msgstr ""
"Najzad, možete sačuvati svoj raspored za štampu unutar datoteke projekta "
"pomoću dugmeta |fileSave| :sup:`Sačuvaj projekat`."

#: ../../docs/user_manual/print_layout/overview_layout.rst:876
msgid "fileSave"
msgstr "fileSave"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/print_layout/overview_layout.rst:64
msgid ""
"You can add multiple elements to the print layout. It is also possible to "
"have more than one map view or legend or scale bar in the print layout "
"canvas, on one or several pages. Each element has its own properties and, in"
" the case of the map, its own extent. If you want to remove any elements "
"from the layout canvas, you can do that with the :kbd:`Delete` or the "
":kbd:`Backspace` key."
msgstr ""
"Možete dodati više elemenata u raspored za štampu. Takođe je moguće imati "
"više od jednog prikaza karte ili legende ili razmernika na platnu rasporeda "
"za štampu, na jednoj ili više strana. Svaki element ima svoja svojstva i, u "
"slučaju karte, svoj obuhvat. Ako želite da uklonite bilo koje elemente sa "
"platna rasporeda, to možete uraditi tasterom :kbd:`Delete` ili "
":kbd:`Backspace`."

#: ../../docs/user_manual/print_layout/overview_layout.rst:76
msgid "The Layout Manager"
msgstr "Menadžer rasporeda"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/print_layout/overview_layout.rst:78
msgid ""
"The :guilabel:`Layout Manager` is the main window to manage print layouts in"
" the project. It gives you an overview of existing print layouts and reports"
" in the project and offers tools to:"
msgstr ""
"Prozor :guilabel:`Menadžer rasporeda` je glavni prozor za upravljanje "
"rasporedima za štampu u projektu. Daje vam pregled postojećih rasporeda za "
"štampu i izveštaja u projektu i nudi alatke za:"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/print_layout/overview_layout.rst:82
msgid "search for a layout;"
msgstr "pretragu rasporeda;"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/print_layout/overview_layout.rst:83
msgid ""
"add new print layout or new report from scratch, template or duplicating an "
"existing one;"
msgstr ""
"dodavanje novog rasporeda za štampu ili novog izveštaja od nule, iz šablona "
"ili dupliranjem postojećeg;"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/print_layout/overview_layout.rst:85
msgid "rename or delete any of them;"
msgstr "preimenovanje ili brisanje bilo kog od njih;"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/print_layout/overview_layout.rst:86
msgid "open them in the project."
msgstr "njihovo otvaranje u projektu."

#: ../../docs/user_manual/print_layout/overview_layout.rst:88
msgid "To open the layout manager dialog:"
msgstr "Da biste otvorili dijalog menadžera rasporeda:"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/print_layout/overview_layout.rst:90
msgid ""
"from the main QGIS dialog, select :menuselection:`Project --> Layout "
"Manager...` menu or click on the |layoutManager| :sup:`Layout Manager` "
"button in the :guilabel:`Project Toolbar`;"
msgstr ""
"iz glavnog QGIS dijaloga izaberite meni :menuselection:`Projekat --> "
"Menadžer rasporeda...` ili kliknite na dugme |layoutManager| :sup:`Menadžer "
"rasporeda` u :guilabel:`paleti alatki Projekat`;"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/print_layout/overview_layout.rst:886
msgid "layoutManager"
msgstr "layoutManager"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/print_layout/overview_layout.rst:92
msgid ""
"from a print layout or report dialog, select :menuselection:`Layout --> "
"Layout Manager...` menu or click on the |layoutManager| :sup:`Layout "
"Manager` button in the :guilabel:`Layout Toolbar`."
msgstr ""
"iz dijaloga rasporeda za štampu ili izveštaja izaberite meni "
":menuselection:`Raspored --> Menadžer rasporeda...` ili kliknite na dugme "
"|layoutManager| :sup:`Menadžer rasporeda` u :guilabel:`paleti alatki "
"Raspored`."

#: ../../docs/user_manual/print_layout/overview_layout.rst:101
msgid "The Print Layout Manager"
msgstr "Menadžer rasporeda za štampu"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/print_layout/overview_layout.rst:104
msgid ""
"The layout manager lists in its upper part all the available print layouts "
"or reports in the project with tools to:"
msgstr ""
"Menadžer rasporeda u svom gornjem delu navodi sve dostupne rasporede za "
"štampu ili izveštaje u projektu, sa alatkama za:"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/print_layout/overview_layout.rst:107
msgid ""
"show the selection: you can select multiple reports and/or print layout(s) "
"and open them in one-click. Double-click a name also opens it;"
msgstr ""
"prikaz izbora: možete izabrati više izveštaja i/ili rasporeda za štampu i "
"otvoriti ih jednim klikom. Dvoklik na naziv takođe ga otvara;"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/print_layout/overview_layout.rst:110
msgid ""
"duplicate the selected print layout or report (available only if one item is"
" selected): it creates a new dialog using the selected one as template. "
"You'll be prompted to choose a new title for the new layout;"
msgstr ""
"dupliranje izabranog rasporeda za štampu ili izveštaja (dostupno samo ako je"
" izabrana jedna stavka): pravi novi dijalog koristeći izabrani kao šablon. "
"Biće vam zatraženo da izaberete novi naslov za novi raspored;"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/print_layout/overview_layout.rst:113
msgid ""
"rename the report or layout (available only if one item is selected): you'll"
" be prompted to choose a new title for the layout;"
msgstr ""
"preimenovanje izveštaja ili rasporeda (dostupno samo ako je izabrana jedna "
"stavka): biće vam zatraženo da izaberete novi naslov za raspored;"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/print_layout/overview_layout.rst:115
msgid ""
"remove the layout: the selected print layout(s) will be deleted from the "
"project."
msgstr ""
"uklanjanje rasporeda: izabrani rasporedi za štampu biće obrisani iz "
"projekta."

#: ../../docs/user_manual/print_layout/overview_layout.rst:117
msgid ""
"In the lower part, it's possible to create new print layouts or reports from"
" scratch or a template. By default, QGIS will look for templates in the "
":ref:`user profile <user_profiles>` folder and the application template "
"directories (accessible with the two buttons at the bottom of the frame) but"
" also in any folder declared as :guilabel:`Path(s) to search for extra print"
" templates` in :menuselection:`Settings --> Options --> Layouts`. Found "
"templates are listed in the combobox. Select an item and press the "
":guilabel:`Create` button to generate a new report or print layout."
msgstr ""
"U donjem delu moguće je praviti nove rasporede za štampu ili izveštaje od "
"nule ili iz šablona. Podrazumevano će QGIS tražiti šablone u folderu "
":ref:`korisničkog profila <user_profiles>` i u direktorijumima šablona "
"aplikacije (dostupnim pomoću dva dugmeta na dnu okvira), ali i u bilo kom "
"folderu deklarisanom kao :guilabel:`Putanja(e) za traženje dodatnih šablona "
"za štampu` u :menuselection:`Podešavanja --> Opcije --> Rasporedi`. "
"Pronađeni šabloni se navode u padajućoj listi. Izaberite stavku i pritisnite"
" dugme :guilabel:`Napravi` da biste generisali novi izveštaj ili raspored za"
" štampu."

#: ../../docs/user_manual/print_layout/overview_layout.rst:126
msgid ""
"You can also use layout templates from a custom folder; in that case, select"
" *specific* in the templates drop-down list, browse to the template and "
"press :guilabel:`Create`."
msgstr ""
"Možete koristiti i šablone rasporeda iz prilagođenog foldera; u tom slučaju "
"izaberite *specific* u padajućoj listi šablona, pronađite šablon i "
"pritisnite :guilabel:`Napravi`."

#: ../../docs/user_manual/print_layout/overview_layout.rst:130
msgid "**Creating template-based print layouts from Browser panel**"
msgstr ""
"**Pravljenje rasporeda za štampu na osnovu šablona iz panela Pregledač**"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/print_layout/overview_layout.rst:132
msgid ""
"Drag-and-drop a print layout template :file:`.qpt` file from any file "
"browser onto the map canvas or double-click it in the :ref:`Browser panel "
"<browser_panel>` generates a new print layout from the template."
msgstr ""
"Prevlačenje datoteke šablona rasporeda za štampu :file:`.qpt` iz bilo kog "
"pregledača datoteka na platno karte ili dvoklik na nju u :ref:`panelu "
"Pregledač <browser_panel>` generiše novi raspored za štampu iz šablona."

#: ../../docs/user_manual/print_layout/overview_layout.rst:140
msgid "Menus, tools and panels of the print layout"
msgstr "Meniji, alatke i paneli rasporeda za štampu"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/print_layout/overview_layout.rst:142
msgid ""
"Opening the print layout provides you with a blank canvas that represents "
"the paper surface when using the print option. Initially you find buttons on"
" the left beside the canvas to add print layout items: 2D or 3D map "
"canvases, text labels, images, legends, scale bars, basic shapes, arrows, "
"attribute or simple tables, HTML frames, elevation profiles,... In this "
"toolbar you also find buttons to navigate, zoom in on an area and pan the "
"view on the layout as well as buttons to select any layout item and to move "
"the extents of the map items."
msgstr ""
"Otvaranje rasporeda za štampu pruža vam prazno platno koje predstavlja "
"površinu papira pri korišćenju opcije štampanja. Isprva sa leve strane pored"
" platna nalazite dugmad za dodavanje stavki rasporeda za štampu: 2D ili 3D "
"platna karte, tekstualni natpisi, slike, legende, razmernici, osnovni "
"oblici, strelice, atributske ili jednostavne tabele, HTML okviri, visinski "
"profili... U ovoj paleti alatki takođe nalazite dugmad za navigaciju, "
"uveličavanje oblasti i pomeranje prikaza na rasporedu, kao i dugmad za izbor"
" bilo koje stavke rasporeda i za pomeranje obuhvata stavki karte."

#: ../../docs/user_manual/print_layout/overview_layout.rst:152
msgid ""
":numref:`figure_layout_overview` shows the initial view of the print layout "
"before any elements are added."
msgstr ""
":numref:`figure_layout_overview` prikazuje početni prikaz rasporeda za "
"štampu pre nego što se dodaju bilo koji elementi."

#: ../../docs/user_manual/print_layout/overview_layout.rst:161
msgid "Print Layout"
msgstr "Raspored za štampu"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/print_layout/overview_layout.rst:164
msgid ""
"On the right beside the canvas you find two set of panels. The upper one "
"holds the panels :guilabel:`Items` and :guilabel:`Undo History` and the "
"lower holds the panels :guilabel:`Layout`, :guilabel:`Item properties` and "
":guilabel:`Atlas generation`."
msgstr ""
"Sa desne strane pored platna nalazite dva skupa panela. Gornji sadrži panele"
" :guilabel:`Stavke` i :guilabel:`Istorija opoziva`, a donji sadrži panele "
":guilabel:`Raspored`, :guilabel:`Svojstva stavke` i :guilabel:`Generisanje "
"atlasa`."

#: ../../docs/user_manual/print_layout/overview_layout.rst:169
msgid ""
"The :guilabel:`Items` panel provides a list of all the print layout items "
"added to the canvas and ways to globally interact with them (see "
":ref:`layout_items_panel` for more information)."
msgstr ""
"Panel :guilabel:`Stavke` pruža listu svih stavki rasporeda za štampu dodatih"
" na platno i načine za globalnu interakciju sa njima (za više informacija "
"pogledajte :ref:`layout_items_panel`)."

#: ../../docs/user_manual/print_layout/overview_layout.rst:172
msgid ""
"The :guilabel:`Undo History` panel displays the history of all changes "
"applied to the layout. With a mouse click, it is possible to undo and redo "
"layout steps back and forth to a certain status."
msgstr ""
"Panel :guilabel:`Istorija opoziva` prikazuje istoriju svih izmena "
"primenjenih na raspored. Klikom miša moguće je opozvati i ponoviti korake "
"rasporeda napred i nazad do određenog stanja."

#: ../../docs/user_manual/print_layout/overview_layout.rst:175
msgid ""
"The :guilabel:`Layout` panel allows you to set general parameters to apply "
"to the layout when exporting or working within (see :ref:`layout_panel` for "
"more details);"
msgstr ""
"Panel :guilabel:`Raspored` omogućava vam da postavite opšte parametre koji "
"se primenjuju na raspored pri izvozu ili radu unutar njega (za više detalja "
"pogledajte :ref:`layout_panel`);"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/print_layout/overview_layout.rst:178
msgid ""
"The :guilabel:`Item Properties` panel displays the properties for the "
"selected item. Click the |select| :sup:`Select/Move item` icon to select an "
"item (e.g., legend, scale bar or label) on the canvas. Then click the "
":guilabel:`Item Properties` panel and customize the settings for the "
"selected item (see :ref:`layout_items` for detailed information on each item"
" settings)."
msgstr ""
"Panel :guilabel:`Svojstva stavke` prikazuje svojstva izabrane stavke. "
"Kliknite na ikonu |select| :sup:`Izaberi/pomeri stavku` da biste izabrali "
"stavku (npr. legendu, razmernik ili natpis) na platnu. Zatim kliknite na "
"panel :guilabel:`Svojstva stavke` i prilagodite podešavanja za izabranu "
"stavku (za detaljne informacije o podešavanjima svake stavke pogledajte "
":ref:`layout_items`)."

#: ../../docs/user_manual/print_layout/overview_layout.rst:184
msgid ""
"The :guilabel:`Atlas` panel allows you to enable the generation of an atlas "
"for the current layout and gives access to its parameters (see "
":ref:`atlas_generation` for detailed information on atlas generation usage)."
msgstr ""
"Panel :guilabel:`Atlas` omogućava vam da omogućite generisanje atlasa za "
"trenutni raspored i daje pristup njegovim parametrima (za detaljne "
"informacije o korišćenju generisanja atlasa pogledajte "
":ref:`atlas_generation`)."

#: ../../docs/user_manual/print_layout/overview_layout.rst:189
msgid ""
"In the bottom part of the print layout window, you can find a status bar "
"with mouse position, current page number, a combo box to set the zoom level,"
" the number of selected items if applicable and, in the case of atlas "
"generation, the number of features."
msgstr ""
"U donjem delu prozora rasporeda za štampu nalazite statusnu traku sa "
"položajem miša, brojem trenutne strane, padajućom listom za postavljanje "
"nivoa uvećanja, brojem izabranih stavki ako je primenljivo i, u slučaju "
"generisanja atlasa, brojem objekata."

#: ../../docs/user_manual/print_layout/overview_layout.rst:193
msgid ""
"In the upper part of the print layout window, you can find menus and other "
"toolbars. All print layout tools are available in menus and as icons in a "
"toolbar."
msgstr ""
"U gornjem delu prozora rasporeda za štampu nalazite menije i druge palete "
