#: ../../docs/user_manual/print_layout/overview_layout.rst:458
msgid ""
"The :menuselection:`Settings --> Layout Options...` menu is a shortcut to "
":menuselection:`Settings --> Options --> Layouts` menu of QGIS main canvas. "
"Here, you can set some options that will be used as default on any new print"
" layout:"
msgstr ""
"Meni :menuselection:`Podešavanja --> Opcije rasporeda...` je prečica do "
"menija :menuselection:`Podešavanja --> Opcije --> Rasporedi` glavnog QGIS "
"platna. Ovde možete postaviti neke opcije koje će se koristiti kao "
"podrazumevane na svakom novom rasporedu za štampu:"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/print_layout/overview_layout.rst:462
msgid ":guilabel:`Layout defaults` let you specify the default font to use;"
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Podrazumevane vrednosti rasporeda` omogućavaju vam da zadate "
"podrazumevani font koji se koristi;"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/print_layout/overview_layout.rst:463
msgid ""
"With :guilabel:`Grid appearance`, you can set the grid style and its color. "
"There are three types of grid: **Dots**, **Solid** lines and **Crosses**;"
msgstr ""
"Pomoću :guilabel:`Izgled mreže` možete postaviti stil mreže i njenu boju. "
"Postoje tri tipa mreže: **Tačke**, **Pune** linije i **Krstići**;"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/print_layout/overview_layout.rst:465
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Grid and guide defaults` defines spacing, offset and tolerance of"
" the grid (see :ref:`grid_guides` for more details);"
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Podrazumevane vrednosti mreže i vodilja` definišu razmak, pomeraj"
" i toleranciju mreže (za više detalja pogledajte :ref:`grid_guides`);"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/print_layout/overview_layout.rst:467
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Layout Paths`: to manage list of custom paths to search print "
"templates."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Putanje rasporeda`: za upravljanje listom prilagođenih putanja za"
" traženje šablona za štampu."

#: ../../docs/user_manual/print_layout/overview_layout.rst:469
msgid ""
"The :menuselection:`Settings --> Keyboard Shortcuts...` menu allows you to "
"use the :ref:`shortcuts manager <shortcuts>` in the print layout interface."
msgstr ""
"Meni :menuselection:`Podešavanja --> Prečice na tastaturi...` omogućava vam "
"da koristite :ref:`menadžer prečica <shortcuts>` u interfejsu rasporeda za "
"štampu."

#: ../../docs/user_manual/print_layout/overview_layout.rst:473
msgid "Contextual menus"
msgstr "Kontekstni meniji"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/print_layout/overview_layout.rst:475
msgid ""
"Depending on where you right-click in the print layout dialog, you open a "
"contextual menu with various features:"
msgstr ""
"U zavisnosti od toga gde kliknete desnim tasterom u dijalogu rasporeda za "
"štampu, otvarate kontekstni meni sa raznim mogućnostima:"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/print_layout/overview_layout.rst:478
msgid ""
"Right-click on the menu bar or any toolbar and you get the list of layout "
"panels and toolbars you can enable or disable in one-click."
msgstr ""
"Kliknite desnim tasterom na traku menija ili bilo koju paletu alatki i "
"dobijate listu panela i paleta alatki rasporeda koje možete omogućiti ili "
"onemogućiti jednim klikom."

#: ../../docs/user_manual/print_layout/overview_layout.rst:480
msgid ""
"Right-click over a ruler and you can |checkbox| :guilabel:`Show Guides`, "
"|checkbox| :guilabel:`Snap to Guides`, :guilabel:`Manage Guides...` opening "
"the :ref:`Guides panel <layout_guides_panel>` or :guilabel:`Clear Guides`. "
"It's also possible to hide the rulers."
msgstr ""
"Kliknite desnim tasterom iznad lenjira i možete |checkbox| "
":guilabel:`Prikaži vodilje`, |checkbox| :guilabel:`Lepi za vodilje`, "
":guilabel:`Upravljaj vodiljama...` čime se otvara :ref:`panel Vodilje "
"<layout_guides_panel>` ili :guilabel:`Očisti vodilje`. Takođe je moguće "
"sakriti lenjire."

#: ../../docs/user_manual/print_layout/overview_layout.rst:484
msgid "Right-click in the print layout canvas and:"
msgstr "Kliknite desnim tasterom na platno rasporeda za štampu i:"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/print_layout/overview_layout.rst:486
msgid ""
"You'll be able to :guilabel:`Undo` and :guilabel:`Redo` recent changes, or "
":guilabel:`Paste` any copied item (only available if no item is selected)."
msgstr ""
"Moći ćete da :guilabel:`Opozovete` i :guilabel:`Ponovite` nedavne izmene, "
"ili :guilabel:`Nalepite` bilo koju kopiranu stavku (dostupno samo ako "
"nijedna stavka nije izabrana)."

#: ../../docs/user_manual/print_layout/overview_layout.rst:488
msgid ""
"If you click over a page, you can additionally access the current :ref:`Page"
" Properties <page_properties>` panel or :guilabel:`Remove Page`."
msgstr ""
"Ako kliknete iznad strane, dodatno možete pristupiti panelu trenutnih "
":ref:`Svojstava strane <page_properties>` ili :guilabel:`Ukloni stranu`."

#: ../../docs/user_manual/print_layout/overview_layout.rst:490
msgid ""
"If you click on a selected item then you can cut or copy it as well as open "
"the :ref:`Item Properties <layout_item_options>` panel."
msgstr ""
"Ako kliknete na izabranu stavku, možete je iseći ili kopirati, kao i "
"otvoriti panel :ref:`Svojstva stavke <layout_item_options>`."

#: ../../docs/user_manual/print_layout/overview_layout.rst:492
msgid ""
"If more than one item are selected, then you can either group them and/or "
"ungroup if at least one group is already in the selection."
msgstr ""
"Ako je izabrano više od jedne stavke, možete ih grupisati i/ili razgrupisati"
" ako je bar jedna grupa već u izboru."

#: ../../docs/user_manual/print_layout/overview_layout.rst:494
msgid ""
"Right-click inside a text box or spinbox widget of any layout panel provides"
" edit options to manipulate its content."
msgstr ""
"Klik desnim tasterom unutar tekstualnog polja ili vidžeta brojača bilo kog "
"panela rasporeda pruža opcije uređivanja za manipulaciju njegovim sadržajem."

#: ../../docs/user_manual/print_layout/overview_layout.rst:501
msgid "The Layout Panel"
msgstr "Panel Raspored"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/print_layout/overview_layout.rst:503
msgid ""
"In the :guilabel:`Layout` panel, you can define the global settings of your "
"print layout."
msgstr ""
"U panelu :guilabel:`Raspored` možete definisati globalna podešavanja svog "
"rasporeda za štampu."

#: ../../docs/user_manual/print_layout/overview_layout.rst:510
msgid "Layout Settings in the Print Layout"
msgstr "Podešavanja rasporeda u rasporedu za štampu"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/print_layout/overview_layout.rst:515
msgid "General settings"
msgstr "Opšta podešavanja"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/print_layout/overview_layout.rst:517
msgid ""
"In a print layout, you can use more than one map item. The "
":guilabel:`Reference map` represents the map item to use as the layout's "
"master map. It's assigned as long as there's a map item in the layout. The "
"layout will use this map in any of their properties and variables "
"calculating units or scale. This includes exporting the print layout to "
"georeferenced formats."
msgstr ""
"U rasporedu za štampu možete koristiti više od jedne stavke karte. "
":guilabel:`Referentna karta` predstavlja stavku karte koja se koristi kao "
"glavna karta rasporeda. Dodeljena je sve dok u rasporedu postoji stavka "
"karte. Raspored će koristiti ovu kartu u bilo kom od svojih svojstava i "
"promenljivih pri računanju jedinica ili razmere. Ovo uključuje izvoz "
"rasporeda za štampu u georeferencirane formate."

#: ../../docs/user_manual/print_layout/overview_layout.rst:523
msgid ""
"Moreover, new layout items such as scale bar, legend or north arrow have by "
"default their settings (orientation, displayed layers, scale, ...) bound to "
"the map item they are drawn over, and fall back to the reference map if "
"there is no overlapping map."
msgstr ""
"Osim toga, nove stavke rasporeda kao što su razmernik, legenda ili strelica "
"severa podrazumevano imaju svoja podešavanja (orijentacija, prikazani "
"slojevi, razmera, ...) vezana za stavku karte iznad koje su iscrtane, a "
"vraćaju se na referentnu kartu ako nema preklapajuće karte."

#: ../../docs/user_manual/print_layout/overview_layout.rst:531
msgid "Guides and Grid"
msgstr "Vodilje i mreža"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/print_layout/overview_layout.rst:533
msgid ""
"You can put some reference marks on your paper sheet to help you accurately "
"place some items. These marks can be:"
msgstr ""
"Na svoj list papira možete postaviti neke referentne oznake koje vam pomažu "
"da precizno postavite neke stavke. Ove oznake mogu biti:"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/print_layout/overview_layout.rst:536
msgid ""
"simple horizontal or vertical lines (called **Guides**) put at the position "
"you want (see :ref:`layout_guides_panel` for guides creation)."
msgstr ""
"jednostavne horizontalne ili vertikalne linije (nazvane **Vodilje**) "
"postavljene na položaj koji želite (za pravljenje vodilja pogledajte "
":ref:`layout_guides_panel`)."

#: ../../docs/user_manual/print_layout/overview_layout.rst:538
msgid ""
"or regular **Grid**: a network of horizontal and vertical lines superimposed"
" over the layout."
msgstr ""
"ili pravilna **Mreža**: mreža horizontalnih i vertikalnih linija naneta "
"preko rasporeda."

#: ../../docs/user_manual/print_layout/overview_layout.rst:541
msgid ""
"Settings like :guilabel:`Grid spacing` or :guilabel:`Grid offset` can be "
"adjusted in this group as well as the :guilabel:`Snap tolerance` to use for "
"items. The tolerance is the maximum distance below which the mouse cursor is"
" snapped to a grid or a guide, while moving, resizing or creating an item."
msgstr ""
"Podešavanja kao što su :guilabel:`Razmak mreže` ili :guilabel:`Pomeraj "
"mreže` mogu se prilagoditi u ovoj grupi, kao i :guilabel:`Tolerancija "
"lepljenja` koja se koristi za stavke. Tolerancija je maksimalno rastojanje "
"ispod kojeg se pokazivač miša lepi za mrežu ili vodilju, tokom pomeranja, "
"promene veličine ili pravljenja stavke."

#: ../../docs/user_manual/print_layout/overview_layout.rst:546
msgid ""
"Whether grid or guides should be shown is set in :menuselection:`View` menu."
" There, you can also decide if they might be used to snap layout items. When"
" both a grid line and a guide line are within tolerance of a point, guides "
"will always take precedence - since they have been manually set (hence, "
"assumption that they have been explicitly placed at highly desirable "
"snapping locations, and should be selected over the general grid)."
msgstr ""
"Da li mrežu ili vodilje treba prikazati postavlja se u meniju "
":menuselection:`Prikaz`. Tamo takođe možete odlučiti da li se mogu koristiti"
" za lepljenje stavki rasporeda. Kada su i linija mreže i linija vodilje "
"unutar tolerancije neke tačke, vodilje će uvek imati prednost - pošto su "
"ručno postavljene (dakle, pretpostavka je da su namerno postavljene na veoma"
" poželjne lokacije za lepljenje i da ih treba izabrati umesto opšte mreže)."

#: ../../docs/user_manual/print_layout/overview_layout.rst:555
msgid ""
"In the :menuselection:`Settings --> Layout Options` menu, you can also set "
"the grid and guides parameters exposed above. However, these options will "
"only apply as defaults to new print layouts."
msgstr ""
"U meniju :menuselection:`Podešavanja --> Opcije rasporeda` takođe možete "
"postaviti parametre mreže i vodilja gore izložene. Međutim, ove opcije će se"
" primeniti samo kao podrazumevane na nove rasporede za štampu."

#: ../../docs/user_manual/print_layout/overview_layout.rst:562
msgid "Export settings"
msgstr "Podešavanja izvoza"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/print_layout/overview_layout.rst:564
msgid ""
"You can define a resolution to use for all exported maps in "
":guilabel:`Export resolution`. This setting can then be overridden each time"
" you export a map."
msgstr ""
"Možete definisati rezoluciju koja se koristi za sve izvezene karte u "
":guilabel:`Rezolucija izvoza`. Ovo podešavanje se zatim može zameniti svaki "
"put kada izvozite kartu."

#: ../../docs/user_manual/print_layout/overview_layout.rst:567
msgid ""
"Because of some advanced rendering options (:ref:`blending mode <blend-"
"modes>`, :ref:`effects <draw_effects>`...), a layout item may need "
"rasterization in order to be exported correctly. QGIS will individually "
"rasterize it without forcing every other item to also be rasterized. This "
"allows printing or saving as PostScript or PDF to keep items as much as "
"possible as vectors, e.g. a map item with layer opacity won't force labels, "
"scale bars, etc to be rasterized too. You can however:"
msgstr ""
"Zbog nekih naprednih opcija iscrtavanja (:ref:`režim stapanja <blend-"
"modes>`, :ref:`efekti <draw_effects>`...), stavka rasporeda može zahtevati "
"rasterizaciju da bi bila ispravno izvezena. QGIS će je pojedinačno "
"rasterizovati bez prisiljavanja svake druge stavke da takođe bude "
"rasterizovana. Time se pri štampanju ili čuvanju kao PostScript ili PDF "
"stavke zadržavaju što je više moguće kao vektori, npr. stavka karte sa "
"neprozirnošću sloja neće prisiliti natpise, razmernike itd. da takođe budu "
"rasterizovani. Međutim, možete:"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/print_layout/overview_layout.rst:575
msgid ""
"force all the items to be rasterized checking the |checkbox| "
":guilabel:`Print as raster` box;"
msgstr ""
"prisiliti sve stavke da budu rasterizovane označavanjem polja |checkbox| "
":guilabel:`Štampaj kao raster`;"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/print_layout/overview_layout.rst:576
msgid ""
"or use the opposite option, i.e. :guilabel:`Always export as vectors`, to "
"force the export to keep items as vectors when exported to a compatible "
"format. Note that in some cases, this could cause the output to look "
"different to layout."
msgstr ""
"ili koristiti suprotnu opciju, tj. :guilabel:`Uvek izvezi kao vektore`, da "
"biste prisilili izvoz da zadrži stavke kao vektore pri izvozu u kompatibilan"
" format. Imajte u vidu da u nekim slučajevima to može učiniti da izlaz "
"izgleda drugačije od rasporeda."

#: ../../docs/user_manual/print_layout/overview_layout.rst:580
msgid ""
"Where the format makes it possible (e.g., :file:`.TIF`, :file:`.PDF`) "
"exporting a print layout results by default in a georeferenced file (based "
"on the :guilabel:`Reference map` item in the :guilabel:`General settings` "
"group). For other formats, georeferenced output requires you to generate a "
"world file by checking |checkbox| :guilabel:`Save world file`. The world "
"file is created beside the exported map(s), has the name of the page output "
"with the reference map item and contains information to georeference it "
"easily."
msgstr ""
"Gde format to omogućava (npr. :file:`.TIF`, :file:`.PDF`), izvoz rasporeda "
"za štampu podrazumevano daje georeferenciranu datoteku (na osnovu stavke "
":guilabel:`Referentna karta` u grupi :guilabel:`Opšta podešavanja`). Za "
"druge formate georeferencirani izlaz zahteva da generišete world datoteku "
"označavanjem |checkbox| :guilabel:`Sačuvaj world datoteku`. World datoteka "
"se pravi pored izvezene karte(a), ima naziv izlaza strane sa stavkom "
"referentne karte i sadrži informacije za njeno lako georeferenciranje."

#: ../../docs/user_manual/print_layout/overview_layout.rst:591
msgid "Resize layout to content"
msgstr "Promeni veličinu rasporeda prema sadržaju"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/print_layout/overview_layout.rst:593
msgid ""
"Using the :guilabel:`Resize page` tool in this group, you create a unique "
"page composition whose extent covers the current contents of the print "
"layout (with some optional :guilabel:`margins` around the cropped bounds)."
msgstr ""
"Pomoću alatke :guilabel:`Promeni veličinu strane` u ovoj grupi pravite "
"jedinstvenu kompoziciju strane čiji obuhvat pokriva trenutni sadržaj "
"rasporeda za štampu (sa nekim opcionim :guilabel:`marginama` oko isečenih "
"granica)."

#: ../../docs/user_manual/print_layout/overview_layout.rst:597
msgid ""
"Note that this behavior is different from the :ref:`crop to content "
"<crop_to_content>` option in that all the items are placed on a real and "
"unique page in replacement of all the existing pages."
msgstr ""
"Imajte u vidu da se ovo ponašanje razlikuje od opcije :ref:`iseci prema "
"sadržaju <crop_to_content>` po tome što se sve stavke postavljaju na stvarnu"
" i jedinstvenu stranu koja zamenjuje sve postojeće strane."

#: ../../docs/user_manual/print_layout/overview_layout.rst:601
msgid "Variables"
msgstr "Promenljive"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/print_layout/overview_layout.rst:603
msgid ""
"The :guilabel:`Variables` lists all the variables available at the layout's "
"level (which includes all global and project's variables)."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Promenljive` navode sve promenljive dostupne na nivou rasporeda "
"(što uključuje sve globalne i projektne promenljive)."

#: ../../docs/user_manual/print_layout/overview_layout.rst:606
msgid ""
"It also allows the user to manage layout-level variables. Click the "
"|symbologyAdd| button to add a new custom layout-level variable. Likewise, "
"select a custom layout-level variable from the list and click the "
"|symbologyRemove| button to remove it."
msgstr ""
"Takođe omogućava korisniku da upravlja promenljivama na nivou rasporeda. "
"Kliknite na dugme |symbologyAdd| da biste dodali novu prilagođenu "
"promenljivu na nivou rasporeda. Isto tako, izaberite prilagođenu promenljivu"
" na nivou rasporeda iz liste i kliknite na dugme |symbologyRemove| da biste "
"je uklonili."

#: ../../docs/user_manual/print_layout/overview_layout.rst:926
msgid "symbologyAdd"
msgstr "symbologyAdd"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/print_layout/overview_layout.rst:928
msgid "symbologyRemove"
msgstr "symbologyRemove"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/print_layout/overview_layout.rst:611
msgid ""
"More information on variables usage in the :ref:`General Tools "
"<general_tools_variables>` section."
msgstr ""
"Više informacija o korišćenju promenljivih u odeljku :ref:`Opšte alatke "
"<general_tools_variables>`."

#: ../../docs/user_manual/print_layout/overview_layout.rst:618
msgid "Variables Editor in the Print Layout"
msgstr "Uređivač promenljivih u rasporedu za štampu"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/print_layout/overview_layout.rst:625
msgid "Working with the page properties"
msgstr "Rad sa svojstvima strane"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/print_layout/overview_layout.rst:627
msgid ""
"A layout can be composed of several pages. For instance, a first page can "
"show a map canvas, and a second page can show the attribute table associated"
" with a layer, while a third one shows an HTML frame linking to your "
"organization website. Or you can add many types of items on each page."
msgstr ""
"Raspored se može sastojati od više strana. Na primer, prva strana može "
"prikazivati platno karte, druga strana atributsku tabelu povezanu sa slojem,"
" dok treća prikazuje HTML okvir koji vodi ka sajtu vaše organizacije. Ili na"
" svaku stranu možete dodati mnogo tipova stavki."

#: ../../docs/user_manual/print_layout/overview_layout.rst:634
msgid "Adding a new page"
msgstr "Dodavanje nove strane"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/print_layout/overview_layout.rst:636
msgid ""
"Furthermore, a layout can be made using different size and/or orientation of"
" pages. To add a page, select the |newPage| :guilabel:`Add Pages...` tool "
"from the :menuselection:`Layout` menu or :guilabel:`Layout Toolbar`. The "
":guilabel:`Insert Pages` dialog opens and you are asked to fill:"
msgstr ""
"Osim toga, raspored se može napraviti pomoću različitih veličina i/ili "
"orijentacija strana. Da biste dodali stranu, izaberite alatku |newPage| "
":guilabel:`Dodaj strane...` iz menija :menuselection:`Raspored` ili "
":guilabel:`palete alatki Raspored`. Otvara se dijalog :guilabel:`Umetni "
"strane` i traži se od vas da popunite:"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/print_layout/overview_layout.rst:641
msgid "the number of pages to insert;"
msgstr "broj strana koje se umeću;"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/print_layout/overview_layout.rst:642
msgid ""
"the position of the page(s): before or after a given page or at the end of "
"the print layout;"
msgstr ""
"položaj strana: pre ili posle zadate strane ili na kraju rasporeda za "
"štampu;"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/print_layout/overview_layout.rst:643
msgid ""
"The :guilabel:`Page size`: it could be of a preset format page (``A4``, "
"``B0``, ``Legal``, ``Letter``, ``ANSI A``, ``Arch A`` and their derivatives "
"as well as a resolution type, such as ``1920x1080`` or ``1024x768``) with "
"associated :guilabel:`Orientation` (Portrait or Landscape)."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Veličina strane`: može biti unapred zadati format strane (``A4``,"
" ``B0``, ``Legal``, ``Letter``, ``ANSI A``, ``Arch A`` i njihove izvedenice,"
" kao i tip rezolucije, kao što je ``1920x1080`` ili ``1024x768``) sa "
"pripadajućom :guilabel:`Orijentacijom` (Uspravno ili Položeno)."

#: ../../docs/user_manual/print_layout/overview_layout.rst:648
msgid ""
"The page size can also be of a ``custom`` format; In that case, you'd need "
"to enter its :guilabel:`Width` and :guilabel:`Height` (with locked size "
"ratio if needed) and select the unit to use among ``mm``, ``cm``, ``px``, "
"``pt``, ``in``, ``ft``... Conversion of entered values is automatically "
"applied when switching from one unit to another."
msgstr ""
"Veličina strane može biti i ``custom`` formata; u tom slučaju biste morali "
"da unesete njenu :guilabel:`Širinu` i :guilabel:`Visinu` (sa zaključanim "
"odnosom veličine ako je potrebno) i izaberete jedinicu koja se koristi među "
"``mm``, ``cm``, ``px``, ``pt``, ``in``, ``ft``... Pretvaranje unetih "
"vrednosti se automatski primenjuje pri prelasku iz jedne jedinice u drugu."

#: ../../docs/user_manual/print_layout/overview_layout.rst:660
msgid "Creating a new page in the Print Layout"
msgstr "Pravljenje nove strane u rasporedu za štampu"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/print_layout/overview_layout.rst:664
msgid "Updating page properties"
msgstr "Ažuriranje svojstava strane"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/print_layout/overview_layout.rst:666
msgid ""
"Any page can be later customized through the Page :guilabel:`Item "
"Properties` panel. To access a page's properties, either:"
msgstr ""
"Bilo koja strana može se kasnije prilagoditi kroz panel Svojstva stavke za "
"stranu. Da biste pristupili svojstvima strane, ili:"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/print_layout/overview_layout.rst:669
msgid "Left-click on an empty section of the page"
msgstr "Kliknite levim tasterom na prazan deo strane"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/print_layout/overview_layout.rst:670
msgid "Right-click on a page and select :guilabel:`Page Properties...`."
msgstr ""
"Kliknite desnim tasterom na stranu i izaberite :guilabel:`Svojstva "
"strane...`."

#: ../../docs/user_manual/print_layout/overview_layout.rst:671
msgid ""
"Go to :menuselection:`Layout --> Page properties...` while hovering over the"
" page"
msgstr ""
"Idite na :menuselection:`Raspored --> Svojstva strane...` dok je pokazivač "
"iznad strane"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/print_layout/overview_layout.rst:673
msgid "The :guilabel:`Item Properties` panel opens with settings such as:"
msgstr ""
"Otvara se panel :guilabel:`Svojstva stavke` sa podešavanjima kao što su:"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/print_layout/overview_layout.rst:675
msgid ""
"for layouts with several pages, it displays the active page number and the "
"count of available pages"
msgstr ""
"za rasporede sa više strana, prikazuje broj aktivne strane i broj dostupnih "
"strana"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/print_layout/overview_layout.rst:677
msgid ""
"the :guilabel:`Page size` frame described above. You can modify each "
"property using the data defined override options (see "
":ref:`atlas_data_defined_override` for a use case);"
msgstr ""
"okvir :guilabel:`Veličina strane` opisan gore. Svako svojstvo možete "
"izmeniti pomoću opcija zamene definisane podacima (za slučaj upotrebe "
"pogledajte :ref:`atlas_data_defined_override`);"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/print_layout/overview_layout.rst:680
msgid ""
"the :guilabel:`Background` of the current page using the :ref:`color <color-"
"selector>` or :ref:`symbol <symbol-selector>` you want."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Pozadina` trenutne strane pomoću :ref:`boje <color-selector>` ili"
" :ref:`simbola <symbol-selector>` koje želite."

#: ../../docs/user_manual/print_layout/overview_layout.rst:682
msgid ""
"the :guilabel:`Apply to all Pages` button updates the current page "
"properties to the other existing pages in the layout;"
msgstr ""
"dugme :guilabel:`Primeni na sve strane` ažurira svojstva trenutne strane na "
"druge postojeće strane u rasporedu;"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/print_layout/overview_layout.rst:684
msgid ""
"the |unchecked| :guilabel:`Exclude page from exports` to control whether the"
" current page with its content should be included in the :ref:`layout output"
" <create-output>`;"
msgstr ""
"|unchecked| :guilabel:`Izostavi stranu iz izvoza` za kontrolu da li trenutnu"
" stranu sa njenim sadržajem treba uključiti u :ref:`izlaz rasporeda <create-"
"output>`;"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/print_layout/overview_layout.rst:692
msgid "Page properties dialog"
msgstr "Dijalog svojstava strane"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/print_layout/overview_layout.rst:699
msgid "The Guides Panel"
msgstr "Panel Vodilje"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/print_layout/overview_layout.rst:701
msgid ""
"Guides are vertical or horizontal line references you can place on a layout "
"page to assist you on items placement, when creating, moving or resizing "
"them. To be active, guides require the :menuselection:`View --> Show Guides`"
" and :menuselection:`View --> Snap to Guides` options to be checked. To "
"create a guide, there are two different methods:"
msgstr ""
"Vodilje su vertikalne ili horizontalne linijske reference koje možete "
"postaviti na stranu rasporeda da vam pomognu pri postavljanju stavki, pri "
"njihovom pravljenju, pomeranju ili promeni veličine. Da bi bile aktivne, "
"vodilje zahtevaju da opcije :menuselection:`Prikaz --> Prikaži vodilje` i "
":menuselection:`Prikaz --> Lepi za vodilje` budu označene. Za pravljenje "
"vodilje postoje dva različita metoda:"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/print_layout/overview_layout.rst:707
msgid ""
"if the :menuselection:`View --> Show Rulers` option is set, drag out a ruler"
" and release the mouse button within the page area, at the desired position."
msgstr ""
"ako je postavljena opcija :menuselection:`Prikaz --> Prikaži lenjire`, "
"izvucite lenjir i otpustite taster miša unutar oblasti strane, na željenom "
"položaju."

#: ../../docs/user_manual/print_layout/overview_layout.rst:709
msgid ""
"for more precision, use the :guilabel:`Guides` panel from the "
":menuselection:`View --> Toolbox -->` or by selecting :guilabel:`Manage "
"guides for page...` from the page's contextual menu."
msgstr ""
"za veću preciznost, koristite panel :guilabel:`Vodilje` iz "
":menuselection:`Prikaz --> Kutija sa alatkama -->` ili izborom "
":guilabel:`Upravljaj vodiljama za stranu...` iz kontekstnog menija strane."

#: ../../docs/user_manual/print_layout/overview_layout.rst:717
msgid "The Guides panel"
msgstr "Panel Vodilje"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/print_layout/overview_layout.rst:719
msgid ""
"The :guilabel:`Guides` panel allows creation of snap lines at specific "
"locations:"
msgstr ""
"Panel :guilabel:`Vodilje` omogućava pravljenje linija za lepljenje na "
"određenim lokacijama:"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/print_layout/overview_layout.rst:721
msgid "Select the :guilabel:`Page` you'd like to add the guides to"
msgstr "Izaberite :guilabel:`Stranu` na koju želite da dodate vodilje"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/print_layout/overview_layout.rst:722
msgid ""
"Click the |symbologyAdd| :sup:`Add new guide` button and enter the "
"coordinates of the horizontal or vertical line. The origin is at the top "
"left corner. Different units are available for this."
msgstr ""
"Kliknite na dugme |symbologyAdd| :sup:`Dodaj novu vodilju` i unesite "
"koordinate horizontalne ili vertikalne linije. Ishodište je u gornjem levom "
"uglu. Za ovo su dostupne različite jedinice."

#: ../../docs/user_manual/print_layout/overview_layout.rst:726
msgid ""
"The panel also allows adjusting the position of existing guides to exact "
"coordinates: double-click and replace the value."
msgstr ""
"Panel takođe omogućava prilagođavanje položaja postojećih vodilja na tačne "
"koordinate: dvokliknite i zamenite vrednost."

#: ../../docs/user_manual/print_layout/overview_layout.rst:728
msgid ""
"The :guilabel:`Guides` panel lists only the items for the current page. It "
"allows creation or removal of guides only in the current page. However, you "
"can use the :guilabel:`Apply to All Pages` button to replicate the guide "
"configuration of the current page to the other pages in the layout."
msgstr ""
"Panel :guilabel:`Vodilje` navodi samo stavke za trenutnu stranu. Omogućava "
"pravljenje ili uklanjanje vodilja samo na trenutnoj strani. Međutim, možete "
"koristiti dugme :guilabel:`Primeni na sve strane` da biste replikovali "
"konfiguraciju vodilja trenutne strane na druge strane u rasporedu."

#: ../../docs/user_manual/print_layout/overview_layout.rst:732
msgid ""
"To delete a guide, select it and press the |symbologyRemove| :sup:`Remove "
"selected guide` button. Use :guilabel:`Clear All Guides` to remove all the "
"guides in the current page."
msgstr ""
"Da biste obrisali vodilju, izaberite je i pritisnite dugme |symbologyRemove|"
" :sup:`Ukloni izabranu vodilju`. Koristite :guilabel:`Očisti sve vodilje` da"
" biste uklonili sve vodilje na trenutnoj strani."

#: ../../docs/user_manual/print_layout/overview_layout.rst:735
msgid "**Snapping to existing layout items**"
msgstr "**Lepljenje za postojeće stavke rasporeda**"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/print_layout/overview_layout.rst:737
msgid ""
"Other than guides and grids, you can use existing items as snapping "
"references when moving, resizing or creating new items; these are called "
"**smart guides** and require :menuselection:`View --> Smart Guides` option "
"to be checked. Anytime the mouse pointer is close to an item's bound, a "
"snapping cross appears."
msgstr ""
"Osim vodilja i mreža, postojeće stavke možete koristiti kao reference za "
"lepljenje pri pomeranju, promeni veličine ili pravljenju novih stavki; one "
"se nazivaju **pametne vodilje** i zahtevaju da opcija :menuselection:`Prikaz"
" --> Pametne vodilje` bude označena. Svaki put kada je pokazivač miša blizu "
"granice neke stavke, pojavljuje se krstić za lepljenje."

#: ../../docs/user_manual/print_layout/overview_layout.rst:746
msgid "The Items Panel"
msgstr "Panel Stavke"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/print_layout/overview_layout.rst:748
msgid ""
"The :guilabel:`Items` panel offers some options to manage selection and "
"visibility of items. All the items added to the print layout canvas "
"(including :ref:`items group <group_items>`) are shown in a list and "
"selecting an item makes the corresponding row selected in the list as well "
"as selecting a row does select the corresponding item in the print layout "
"canvas. This is thus a handy way to select an item placed behind another "
"one. Note that a selected row is shown as bold. Multiple items selection is "
"also possible holding :kbd:`Shift` for contiguous items, and :kbd:`Ctrl` key"
" for non-contiguous ones."
msgstr ""
"Panel :guilabel:`Stavke` nudi neke opcije za upravljanje izborom i "
"vidljivošću stavki. Sve stavke dodate na platno rasporeda za štampu "
"(uključujući :ref:`grupu stavki <group_items>`) prikazane su u listi, a "
"izbor stavke čini odgovarajući red izabranim u listi, kao što i izbor reda "
"bira odgovarajuću stavku na platnu rasporeda za štampu. Ovo je stoga zgodan "
"način za izbor stavke postavljene iza druge. Imajte u vidu da je izabran red"
" prikazan podebljano. Izbor više stavki takođe je moguć držanjem "
":kbd:`Shift` za susedne stavke i tastera :kbd:`Ctrl` za nesusedne."

#: ../../docs/user_manual/print_layout/overview_layout.rst:758
msgid "For any available item, you can:"
msgstr "Za bilo koju dostupnu stavku možete:"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/print_layout/overview_layout.rst:760
msgid "|showAllLayers| set it visible or not;"
msgstr "|showAllLayers| postaviti je vidljivom ili ne;"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/print_layout/overview_layout.rst:924
msgid "showAllLayers"
msgstr "showAllLayers"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/print_layout/overview_layout.rst:761
msgid "|locked| lock or unlock its position;"
msgstr "|locked| zaključati ili otključati njen položaj;"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/print_layout/overview_layout.rst:762
msgid ""
"sort its Z position. You can move up and down each item in the list with a "
"click and drag. The upper item in the list will be brought to the foreground"
" in the print layout canvas. By default, a newly created item is placed in "
"the foreground."
msgstr ""
"sortirati njen Z položaj. Svaku stavku u listi možete pomeriti gore i dole "
"klikom i prevlačenjem. Gornja stavka u listi biće dovedena u prvi plan na "
"platnu rasporeda za štampu. Podrazumevano se novonapravljena stavka "
"postavlja u prvi plan."

#: ../../docs/user_manual/print_layout/overview_layout.rst:765
msgid "change the item ID by double-clicking the text;"
msgstr "promeniti ID stavke dvoklikom na tekst;"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/print_layout/overview_layout.rst:766
msgid ""
"right-click an item and select whether to copy or delete it or open its "
":ref:`properties panel <layout_item_options>`."
msgstr ""
"kliknuti desnim tasterom na stavku i izabrati da li da je kopirate ili "
"obrišete ili otvorite njen :ref:`panel svojstava <layout_item_options>`."

#: ../../docs/user_manual/print_layout/overview_layout.rst:769
msgid ""
"Once you have found the correct position for an item, you can lock it by "
"ticking the box in |locked| column. Locked items are **not** selectable on "
"the canvas. Locked items can be unlocked by selecting the item in the "
":menuselection:`Items` panel and unchecking the tickbox or you can use the "
"icons on the toolbar."
msgstr ""
"Kada pronađete ispravan položaj za stavku, možete je zaključati označavanjem"
" polja u koloni |locked|. Zaključane stavke **nisu** izborljive na platnu. "
"Zaključane stavke mogu se otključati izborom stavke u panelu "
":menuselection:`Stavke` i poništavanjem polja ili možete koristiti ikone u "
"paleti alatki."

#: ../../docs/user_manual/print_layout/overview_layout.rst:780
msgid "The Undo History Panel: Revert and Restore actions"
msgstr "Panel Istorija opoziva: radnje opoziva i ponavljanja"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/print_layout/overview_layout.rst:782
msgid ""
"During the layout process, it is possible to revert and restore changes. "
"This can be done with the revert and restore tools available in the "
":guilabel:`Edit` menu, the :guilabel:`Layout` toolbar or the contextual menu"
" any time you right-click in the print layout area:"
msgstr ""
"Tokom procesa rasporeda moguće je opozvati i ponoviti izmene. To se može "
"uraditi pomoću alatki za opoziv i ponavljanje dostupnih u meniju "
":guilabel:`Uređivanje`, paleti alatki :guilabel:`Raspored` ili kontekstnom "
"meniju svaki put kada kliknete desnim tasterom u oblasti rasporeda za "
"štampu:"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/print_layout/overview_layout.rst:787
msgid "|undo| :sup:`Revert last change`"
msgstr "|undo| :sup:`Opozovi poslednju izmenu`"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/print_layout/overview_layout.rst:788
msgid "|redo| :sup:`Restore last change`"
msgstr "|redo| :sup:`Ponovi poslednju izmenu`"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/print_layout/overview_layout.rst:790
msgid ""
"This can also be done by mouse click within the :guilabel:`Undo history` "
"panel (see :numref:`figure_layout`). The History panel lists the last "
"actions done within the print layout. Select the point you want to revert to"
" and once you do a new action all the actions done after the selected one "
"will be removed."
msgstr ""
"To se takođe može uraditi klikom miša unutar panela :guilabel:`Istorija "
"opoziva` (pogledajte :numref:`figure_layout`). Panel Istorija navodi "
"poslednje radnje obavljene unutar rasporeda za štampu. Izaberite tačku na "
"koju želite da se vratite i kada obavite novu radnju, sve radnje obavljene "
"posle izabrane biće uklonjene."

